    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/364f16d68dab576d312c8763d541ca2b.avif?t=1771407975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras_big/364f16d68dab576d312c8763d541ca2b.avif?t=1771407975 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/28c8132ada9e0b17f32ce8b941184ebd.poster.avif?t=1771407975\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/28c8132ada9e0b17f32ce8b941184ebd.webm?t=1771407975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你可以逃离潜伏在黑暗中的恐怖……但永远无法逃离内心深处的恐惧</strong>。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《血色使徒》是一款叙事性密室逃脱游戏，作为小说《德古拉》的前传。你将扮演伦菲尔德，一个被悔恨与疯狂夹缝困住的人。为了生存，你必须解谜，面对令人不安的幻象，并克服神秘的格拉茨伯爵夫人多林根所施加的试炼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索德古拉神话中最令人不安角色的起源，揭开塑造他命运的恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/f18df34305506e54a2858a0133440437.avif?t=1771407975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras_big/f18df34305506e54a2858a0133440437.avif?t=1771407975 width=800 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/56cf7f8d4a48d7f42ad2a7507577d6f9.poster.avif?t=1771407975\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/56cf7f8d4a48d7f42ad2a7507577d6f9.webm?t=1771407975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开复杂的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查环境，解开谜题，并利用逻辑与观察逃离封闭的房间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离侵蚀主角理智的幻象。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离随时可能打断谜题的怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验德古拉神秘仆人的起源。发现野心与疯狂如何引导他走向命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras/1ade9337efcc956ad9163e781bfdb350.avif?t=1771407975\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307230/extras_big/1ade9337efcc956ad9163e781bfdb350.avif?t=1771407975 width=800 height=89 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
